{
  "texts": [
    "Dotted lines indicate the possibility morphism h, while a solid line from s down to t indicates that t is a refinement of s. Fact 33.4 (Strict Conditions & Matching Conditions).",
    "For any possibility frames F and F ′ and h: F → F ′:1.",
    "⊑-forth implies the left-to-right direction of ⊑-matching;2.",
    "⊑-back implies the right-to-left direction of ⊑-matching;3.",
    "R-forth implies the left-to-right direction of R-matching; 4."
  ]
}